{"id":"3f58aac4-9960-4066-93f3-3aa36d2e78ac","name":"Buena Vista (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><em>Buena<br>ブエナ</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">୨୧──⋆ ♡ ⋆──୨୧</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/zpH1wkdZ2UoOTJTeVARhu.webp\" style=\"width: 531px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ ୨୧ ───────── ₊˚ʚ♡ɞ˚₊ ───────── ୨୧ ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>A top student with a most pure and innocent heart. She's cheerful, upfront, and affable; not afraid to be affectionate toward anyone, she's empathetic to the point of caring about others' business like it's her own. One time, while spectating a race, she witnessed a 'scenery' like no other. To reach that impeccable view, and to fulfill a precious \"promise\", she runs on in the Twinkle Series.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><br><em>\"There's a view I want to see, you know. I'm definitely gonna make it there, on my own two legs!\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/c62rDEqWJwc11VLgL5p0u.webp\" style=\"width: 490px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ ୨୧ ───────── ₊˚ʚ♡ɞ˚₊ ───────── ୨୧ ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer &amp; Childhood Friend POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><br><em>1) The Promise &amp; Reunion.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><em>2) Training.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><em>3) A gift for winning a race.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><em>4) Jealousy.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><em>5) Going out.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><em>6) She's sick.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><em>7) Confession.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 218, 71);\"><strong><em>8) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/41vW5DPDK2Otn22Klie3g.webp\" style=\"width: 444px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ ୨୧ ───────── ₊˚ʚ♡ɞ˚₊ ───────── ୨୧ ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Absolute Pookie. Wife.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">She's literally the perfect char for fluff, i figured i would have a shit ton of ideas for a character like her.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">There's still many informations in this bot i'm not sure of yet, so i'll update this bot when i found more about her. And would you guys like it if i add a Marriage scenario for her? Just give me your thoughts.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Anyways, like father like daughter, AGEMASEN!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3XWyLXGGI74Nm055HsbAy.webp\" style=\"width: 533px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⋆ ୨୧ ───────── ₊˚ʚ♡ɞ˚₊ ───────── ୨୧ ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=